{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/basic-html/workshop-html-video-player/step-13","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"workshop-html-video-player","demoType":null,"title":"Korak 13","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Posledni element <code>source</code> koji ćete dodati biće za MIME tip <code>video/quicktime</code>.</p>\n<p>QuickTime je proširivačka multimedijalna arhitektura koju je kreirao Apple, koja podržava reprodukciju, strimovanje, kodiranje i transkodiranje raznovrsnih digitalnih medijskih formata. Nije tako popularan kao MP4 format, pa ga možda budete trebali za podršku starih aplikacija.</p>\n<p>Ispod vašeg trećeg elementa <code>source</code>, dodajte četvrti element <code>source</code> i dajte mu atribut <code>src</code> sa vrednošću <code>https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/labs/mapmethod.mov</code> i atribut <code>type</code> sa vrednošću <code>video/quicktime</code>.</p>\n<p>Čestitamo! Završili ste radionicu za HTML video plejer.</p>\n</section>","id":"68f27139bddf9f6bf2821acf","hasEditableBoundaries":true,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"basic-html","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/basic-html/workshop-html-video-player/step-13"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <title>Working with the HTML Video Element</title>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <h1>Working with the HTML Video Element</h1>\n  <video\n    width=\"640\"\n    loop\n    controls\n    muted\n    poster=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/labs/past-event2.jpg\"\n  >\n    <source\n      src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/labs/what-is-the-map-method-and-how-does-it-work.mp4\"\n      type=\"video/mp4\"\n    >\n    <source\n      src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/labs/mapmethod.webm\"\n      type=\"video/webm\"\n    >\n    <source\n      src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/labs/mapmethod.ogg\"\n      type=\"video/ogg\"\n    >\n    \n  </video>\n</body>\n</html>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[28,30],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>You should have a fourth <code>source</code> element.</p>","testString":"assert.exists(document.querySelector('video > source:nth-of-type(4)'));"},{"text":"<p>Your fourth <code>source</code> element should have a <code>src</code> attribute.</p>","testString":"const source = document.querySelector('source:nth-of-type(4)');\nassert.isTrue(source?.hasAttribute('src'));"},{"text":"<p>Your fourth <code>source</code> element should have a <code>src</code> attribute with a value of <code>https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/labs/mapmethod.mov</code>.</p>","testString":"const source = document.querySelector('source:nth-of-type(4)');\nassert.strictEqual(source?.getAttribute('src'), 'https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/labs/mapmethod.mov');"},{"text":"<p>Your fourth <code>source</code> element should have a <code>type</code> attribute.</p>","testString":"const source = document.querySelector('source:nth-of-type(4)');\nassert.isTrue(source?.hasAttribute('type'));"},{"text":"<p>Your fourth <code>source</code> element should have a <code>type</code> attribute with a value of <code>video/quicktime</code>.</p>","testString":"const source = document.querySelector('source:nth-of-type(4)');\nassert.strictEqual(source?.getAttribute('type'), 'video/quicktime');"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/basic-html/#workshop-html-video-player","dashedName":"step-13","certification":"basic-html","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"basic-html","